    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A fine mortar or cement made of lime and water, slaked with water and aged, often mixed with sand or marble dust to make the several types of lime plasters, grouts, mortars, and limewash.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
